---
title: Chorizo & Tomato Penne with Roasted Red Pepper
description: Chorizo is THE sausage of Spain, and is often paired with crusty bread, eggs or sweet tomatoes to balance the bold flavours of the sausage. We think red pepper and tomatoes does the trick perfectly, and a sprinkle of sharp Parmesan is the finishing touch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-chorizo-tomato-penne-2477fc0f.jpg
